Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn such light, smooth clothes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:01:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those are the details of the plot Claudia McCunnen has weaved so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She trapped me in order to bring me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,persuaded Zwei, who became Phantom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and seized Wisemel's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One can only say that her way of handling things is simply superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie Garland contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia McCunnen has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she isn't going to show up and give excuses on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's hard to believe, Scythe Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think we could see this as the proof of your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should keep collaborating with the Godo Family who supported Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cocaine robbery from a year ago surely is a painful memory to Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the profit from the market run by the Godo Family in the Far East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is several times greater than the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, if we are to put rational arguments aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please give consideration to the excellent decision of Mr. Shiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who disciplined his own people as soon as he learned the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It is, indeed, a reasonable suggestion. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll have the Godo Family reduce the margin they were demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the penalty for this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then Mr. Shiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With regards to Claudia McCunnen, who enticed your brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we promise she will receive the cruelest of punishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much Mr. McGwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently investigating where Claudia ran off to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the question is Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will that man do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay Mr. McGwire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I send Ein to pursue him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A confrontation between the current and the previous Phantom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting we become subordinate to the Bloodies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like Romero was killed by Isaac himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bloodies are now being backed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a newer, stronger organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days, the era of Inferno will come without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to push your way to the top that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd even sell yourself to the one who killed your little brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to where Romero couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that doing so is the best thing I can do for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with me, Lizzie Garland. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm a gangster, but I have no intention of becoming depraved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a code of conduct that I can't compromise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one more important than acting out of self interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you swear that you won't cross that line...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then yeah, Clo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You jumped the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck. I can't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Contact Lizzie. Tell her that nothing turned up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the key to that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This car always looks so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't often get a chance like this. I wish we could've had the owner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji... Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you know the situation more or less, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to justify myself to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done the best I could all this time to survive in the organization. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've paid you a reasonable compensation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still recover, Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I'm with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave LA and join an organization on the east coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to protect myself from Inferno's pursuers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you at that drive-in on route 39.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time for real, I'm entrusting you with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such minor scars can be removed anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I purposely did not allow such treatment. Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do those scars mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humiliation and corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein, you were my masterpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you were tainted by that man twice in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far from perfection right now. You're trash that's hard to even look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, I kept you, wrecked, by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I thought that reformation might be possible when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Avenge your defeats with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you restore yourself on your own and take back the brilliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have those scars removed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll once again love you as my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Ein be able to defeat Reiji Azuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When push comes to shove,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll finish off Zwei even if they end up stabbing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without hesitating to sacrifice her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're going to dispose of her after all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By having gained Ein, an experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my art is about to advance to an even higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's memorable as my first completed work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't find much value in a monument, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as it is the final stage, you could've used a more reliable method.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes an actor's acting exceeds the director's direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes the paintbrush moves in an unexpected way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprising both, the artist and the audience...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mischief caused by the Muses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the finale be a tragedy... or a comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrusting the plot of the finale to fate is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a great thrill that causes your heart to race, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't killing her too much for you, Lizzie Garland?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me. Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Claudia have known each other for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might become emotional and hesitate to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls don't like guys who aren't on time, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not called... Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... have I been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep running like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so fast that no one can catch up, leaving everything behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll eventually fly away into the sky, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be really wonderful. That's real freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far were you planning to go by taking such huge risks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a set goal. I'll just go as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get tired from running someday and stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not standing on the ground then, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must've been some things that you shouldn't have left behind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were sceneries that you could see only when you run with this speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to chase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to die like this without doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting against you is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be a problem for me. I was ordered to fight and achieve victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to prove that I am the strongest one... the one and only Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see. If that's the case, I'll go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're still given...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reasons that you can fiercely fight for like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by that Scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor do I think that I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had... enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I could kill you and escape from this situation, what do I do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will change?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being lied to and manipulated, I can't even protect what I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this repetition any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please... finish it this time for sure... with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't blame you. I don't think it can be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surely couldn't bear it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're surviving and still fighting... even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for that Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My reason for living is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to fight of my own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mark you engraved then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admired your strength on that day, although it was a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evidence of your promise remains on my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I couldn't give up on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking my place, you walked the path that I gave up on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while fighting... and resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've lived dreaming of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that even now, my other self is living strongly and freely somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scar always reminded me of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way that I can bear such a pain forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to give up, no one can blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're going to break your promise from that day... first eliminate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm Master's failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a puppet that's just waiting to be discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason this world isn't an endless hell
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to live in a world without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until today, I couldn't keep any promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if my promise is still alive here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I want to keep at least that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be, for sure, my last...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you away from Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things seem to have turned out in a very disappointing manner indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could also be just an intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... I can't go to the world where you're waiting for me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have unfinished business to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we'd never be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
